CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1781790493
OL,3,CTeacher sentenced to whole life term
OL,4,Cfor 'sadistic' murder of adopted baby
OL,6,FA high school teacher has been handed
OL,7,Fa whole life term for the "sadistic"
OL,8,Fmurder and sexual abuse of his adopted
OL,9,Fbaby.
OL,11,FJamie Varley, 37, adopted Preston
OL,12,FDavey at nine-months-old with his
OL,13,Fpartner John McGowan-Fazakerley, 32,
OL,14,Fbefore treating him as his
OL,15,F"plaything", sexually assaulting and
OL,16,Fphysically abusing him.
OL,18,FJust four months later Varley murdered
OL,19,Fthe baby boy, following a sexual
OL,20,Fassault, at their Blackpool home.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,362,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1781790493
OL,3,CTeacher sentenced to whole life term
OL,4,Cfor 'sadistic' murder of adopted baby
OL,6,FSentencing Varley at Preston Crown
OL,7,FCourt, Mr Justice Turner said 13-month-
OL,8,Fold Preston had faced "unremitting
OL,9,Fabuse" and neglect.
OL,11,FTurning to Varley, he said: "It was
OL,12,Fyou who did this. You murdered him.
OL,14,F"A whole life order is a sentence of
OL,15,Flast resort for cases of the most
OL,16,Fextreme gravity.
OL,18,F"This is a case of the most extreme
OL,19,Fgravity. You must stay in prison for
OL,20,Fthe rest of your life. You will never
OL,21,Fbe eligible for parole."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,362,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1781790493
OL,3,CTeacher sentenced to whole life term
OL,4,Cfor 'sadistic' murder of adopted baby
OL,6,FA whole life order is the most severe
OL,7,Fand rare punishment a criminal court
OL,8,Fcan impose on a defendant in the UK.
OL,9,FThis means they will never be released
OL,10,Ffrom prison.
OL,12,FThere are believed to be only around
OL,13,F70 whole-life prisoners in British
OL,14,Fprisons, including Lucy Letby and
OL,15,FWayne Couzens.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,362,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1781790493
OL,3,CTeacher sentenced to whole life term
OL,4,Cfor 'sadistic' murder of adopted baby
OL,6,FMcGowan-Fazakerley was also jailed for
OL,7,F25 years for sexual assault and
OL,8,Fallowing the death of his adopted baby
OL,9,Fon 27 April 2023 after both were
OL,10,Fconvicted following an eight-week
OL,11,Ftrial.
OL,13,FThe trial revealed the abuse Preston
OL,14,Fsuffered at the hands of Varley and
OL,15,FMcGowan-Fazakerley.
OL,17,FA jury heard how Preston was routinely
OL,18,Fill-treated, physically assaulted, and
OL,19,Fsexually abused while in their care
OL,20,Ffor just under four months at their
OL,21,Fhome in Blackpool.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,362,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1781790493
OL,3,CTeacher sentenced to whole life term
OL,4,Cfor 'sadistic' murder of adopted baby
OL,6,FPreston had been taken from his
OL,7,Fmother, Sarah Davey, now 42, by an
OL,8,Femergency care order by Oldham Council.
OL,10,FMs Davey, when she was 14, had been
OL,11,Fjailed for the "unspeakably wicked"
OL,12,Fmurder of a frail pensioner in 1998
OL,13,Fand had been in and out of prison
OL,14,Fsince then.
OL,16,FIn a victim impact statement, Ms Davey
OL,17,Fdescribed the day Preston was taken
OL,18,Ffrom her as one of the worst of her
OL,19,Flife.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,362,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1781790493
OL,3,CTeacher sentenced to whole life term
OL,4,Cfor 'sadistic' murder of adopted baby
OL,6,FShe said: "I will never forgive you
OL,7,Ffor what you did to my son and what
OL,8,Fyou stopped him from becoming and
OL,9,Fachieving in his life."
OL,11,FMr Justice Turner said Varley's
OL,12,F"growing and selfish resentment
OL,13,Ftowards Preston" played a part in him
OL,14,Fabusing the youngster.
OL,16,FHe added Varley's "professional
OL,17,Fbackground as a teacher together with
OL,18,Fyour charm and easy manner" was used
OL,19,Fto reassure others all was well.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,362,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1781790493
OL,3,CTeacher sentenced to whole life term
OL,4,Cfor 'sadistic' murder of adopted baby
OL,6,FChildren's Children's Commissioner
OL,7,FDame Rachel De Souza said the murder
OL,8,Fof 13-month-old Preston Davey was a
OL,9,F"massive safeguarding failure."
OL,11,F"We know that very early into his
OL,12,Fadoption, he was taken to hospital
OL,13,Fwith bruises.
OL,15,F"The consultant dismissed it. Did they
OL,16,Fdismiss it because it was a teacher
OL,17,Fadopter?
OL,19,F"Did that evil abuser hoodwink people
OL,20,Funder that professional guise?
OL,26,@qD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,362,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36108
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1781790493
OL,3,CTeacher sentenced to whole life term
OL,4,Cfor 'sadistic' murder of adopted baby
OL,6,F"The social worker saw him 20 days
OL,7,Fbefore he died, I want to know whether
OL,8,Fthe correct level of professional
OL,9,Fcuriosity was there.
OL,11,F"I have huge numbers of questions, and
OL,12,FI'm not going to let go until I have
OL,13,Fthe answers."
OL,15,FDame Rachel De Souza has called on the
OL,16,FGovernment to establish a Child
OL,17,FProtection Authority "today", adding
OL,18,Fthe state failed Preston Davey.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,362,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36109
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1781790493
OL,3,CTeacher sentenced to whole life term
OL,4,Cfor 'sadistic' murder of adopted baby
OL,6,FShe said: "My demand today to the
OL,7,FGovernment is, get it open today. That
OL,8,Fis what we need.
OL,10,F"We need a child protection authority
OL,11,Fwith teeth to actually hold
OL,12,Faccountability and make sure the
OL,13,Fsystem isn't fragmented, and to be
OL,14,Fable to point to 'you are accountable
OL,15,Ffor this child'."
OL,17,FA government spokesperson said: "This
OL,18,Fis a sickening case of evil abusers
OL,19,Fexploiting a vulnerable child.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,362,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36110
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1781790493
OL,3,CTeacher sentenced to whole life term
OL,4,Cfor 'sadistic' murder of adopted baby
OL,6,F"The public rightly demand answers
OL,7,Fabout what went wrong and we can
OL,8,Fassure them we will make sure anyone
OL,9,Fresponsible for negligence faces
OL,10,Fconsequences.
OL,12,F"This is exactly why this government
OL,13,Fhas brought in the most far-reaching
OL,14,Fchild protection reforms in a
OL,15,Fgeneration, including with a new law,
OL,16,Fthe Children's Wellbeing and Schools
OL,17,FAct, which requires social workers,
OL,18,Fhealth professionals and the police to
OL,19,Fwork together better to protect
OL,20,Fvulnerable children at risk of abuse.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,362,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36111
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1781790493
OL,3,CTeacher sentenced to whole life term
OL,4,Cfor 'sadistic' murder of adopted baby
OL,6,F"We are also introducing a new Child
OL,7,FProtection Authority in England to
OL,8,Foversee the national picture.
OL,10,F"An independent review has been
OL,11,Fcommissioned by the local authorities
OL,12,Fand the independent national Child
OL,13,FSafeguarding Practice Review Panel
OL,14,Fwill work with them to get to the
OL,15,Fbottom of this horrifying case."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
